Magna Carta Health is a preventive digital health organization focused on preventing death , disability and disease with the aid of technology.

Book a Consultation with Us!

Who we are

MCH is bridging the gap between substandard and optimal health care by providing personalized and integrated health care access and coaching.

Our approach is to build and enable a clinically integrated network using technology, team-based care and a unique disease management and prevention approach.

Learn More

Improved Access

 We provide increased healthcare access and improved healthcare services through integrated disease management and population health tools.

Improved Outcomes

 We believe that the best way to improve health outcomes is to engage and empower patients to be responsible for their own health. Our PCMH approach puts the patients at the center of the healthcare delivery cycle.

Satisfaction Guaranteed

The future of any society depends on the health and well-being of its people. At MCH, we believe that a healthy individual and workforce is the hallmark of a better tomorrow. Visit our clinic for health and medical services to see a doctor today.
